हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: When billionaire CEO Rudra Raychand’s one-night encounter with spirited lawyer Akanksha leads to a forgotten past, secret parentage, and ruthless betrayals from her sister Ekta, their worlds collide in a storm of power, love, and revenge. As hidden truths surface and family bonds are tested, Rudra and Akanksha must fight for love, legacy, and the daughter they never knew they shared. Watch Now!
